    "description": "<br><br>Chillquarium 是一款轻松愉快的放置游戏，在游戏中，你可以购买育苗养育自己的小鱼，等它们随时间长大后再卖掉它们赚取利润，也可以将它们留在鱼缸中获得门票参观的收入。<br><br>购买强化卡包，解锁稀有鱼种！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276930/extras/7d07528be21cf2ea50fa0782b4cb9c89.poster.avif?t=1751390547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276930/extras/7d07528be21cf2ea50fa0782b4cb9c89.webm?t=1751390547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276930/extras/7d07528be21cf2ea50fa0782b4cb9c89.mp4?t=1751390547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>疯狂投喂你的小鱼！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276930/extras/c0d3e1993102fda7dc478fd00aae1428.poster.avif?t=1751390547\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276930/extras/c0d3e1993102fda7dc478fd00aae1428.webm?t=1751390547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276930/extras/c0d3e1993102fda7dc478fd00aae1428.mp4?t=1751390547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当你拥有100种特殊的鱼类，就能解锁小鱼稀有和极稀有的多色形态！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276930/extras/75bf65d1414f8d9853d70650ea4fd65f.poster.avif?t=1751390547\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276930/extras/75bf65d1414f8d9853d70650ea4fd65f.webm?t=1751390547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276930/extras/75bf65d1414f8d9853d70650ea4fd65f.mp4?t=1751390547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>打造属于自己的水族箱，和你的鱼儿们一起在实时的昼夜循环中放松身心吧~<br>",
